Package entity

Class CountryMetricsEntity

java.lang.Object
entity.CountryMetricsEntity
@Entity public class CountryMetricsEntity extends Object
Entity class representing the metrics of a Country for a given day. This class is mapped to the "country_metrics" table and contains details about a country's population, money, happiness, and individual budget for a specific day.

  • Field Details

    • id

      private Long id
      The unique identifier for the Country metrics. This is the primary key of the "country_metrics" table. It is auto-generated using the IDENTITY strategy.

    • day

      private int day
      The day for which the metrics are recorded. This field cannot be null.
